Package com.camerontec.catalys.fixtesttool.command.expression

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConditionalExpressionFactory
    Interface for factory implementations capable of creating concrete Expressions based on the specified expression specification.
    Expression
    Interface to be implemented by classes capable of representing general expressions.
    ValueExpressionFactory
    Interface to be implemented by classes capable of creation concrete Expressions for resolving Field#values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotatedExpressionFactory
    Factory class for creating concrete expressions based on their MatchingRegexp annotations.
    FieldResolver
    Base class for resolving raw Field instances.
    FIXNestedNumInGroupExpression
    Class for resolving nested number in group tag expressions.
    FIXNestedRepeatingGroupExpression
    Class for resolving nested repeating group tag expressions.
    FIXRepeatingGroupExpression
    Base class for evaluating repeating group tag expressions.
    FIXRepeatingGroupExpressionFactory
    Factory for creating the appropriate concrete FIXRepeatingGroupExpression based on the specified repeating group expression.
    FIXStringValueExpression
    Expression for evaluating FIX values expressed as Strings.
    MessageReferenceValueExpression
    Expression for evaluating references to values in other FIX messages.
    RegexpMatchingValueExpressionFactory
    Factory class for creating concrete expressions for Field#value resolution.
    TagExpressionFieldResolver
    Class for resolving Field tag based expressions.
    ValueExpressionFieldResolver
    Class for resolving Field value based expressions.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    MatchingRegexp
    An annotation to be used by concrete Expression classes for specifying their matching regular expressions.
